{"tid":1681181,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【懲罰系列】樂林小鍋米線","createTime":"2019-10-29T09:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T17:49:28.000Z","uid":202895,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"58859683c9478f86fe42772bf8bdd9fc159538af","tid":1681181,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"今日去咗太古到有野做，咁忙完我就打開我嘅黃藍地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比我發現原來鰂魚涌有間米線好值得懲罰<br />\n佢就係呢間<strong><ins>樂林小鍋米線</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhdxMs4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhdxMs4.jpg&h=b909b332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">地址：鰂魚涌濱海街11號地舖<br />\n(港鐵鰂魚涌站 A 出口, 步行約3分鐘)</span><br />\n<br />\n咁就係箭嘴個間，隔離間茶餐廳好搶眼，差小小比佢呃咗<br />\n咁我有睇下食咩好，睇到佢嘅豬頸肉好出名，咁我就叫黎試下啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Vv4Cz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Vv4Cz2.jpg&h=7d7d5ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我叫咗小麻辣(麻辣額外+2蚊)，豬頸肉米線<br />\n食第一啖覺得佢唔係好麻辣，但係一路食落去就越黎越麻辣，好正<br />\n米線唔係太冧，但豬頸肉就好鬼冧，我自己中意食爽嘅豬頸肉，覺得就普通啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋原來碗米線有半隻滷蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係食食下先睇到，好驚喜，居然有米線鋪係有滷蛋做配菜<br />\n<br />\n對於女仔岩岩好，男仔就未必夠啦<br />\n埋單都係50蚊樓下，對於係港島，呢個價錢我覺得都ok，更何況佢係良心小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比良心事跡作fc，我都親眼睇到學生餐張poster痴係門口到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOFTv25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOFTv25.jpg&h=fc6af491&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e898564ca26b40cf2c673a9471a7b2be66e12d","tid":1681181,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"推 要分散懲罰"},{"pid":"c8645a2c97f20efd2c026e5765ad8fb46ffeded9","tid":1681181,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c679a85579513711c473f08e8409f21189f93a7","tid":1681181,"uid":198343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"Le間野本身lunch已經爆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d050c470da95c887047458b02a7823a5c21ec4b","tid":1681181,"uid":202895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c679a85579513711c473f08e8409f21189f93a7","tid":1681181,"uid":198343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"Le間野本身lunch已經爆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"大西北友唔知道<br />\n下次去個頭會換第二間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab3aed51838fdfffb2292e63439b4706324016f","tid":1681181,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cff8b869f909f397b8e973c8e4c7529bae4e2b","tid":1681181,"uid":331682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"Gogogo"},{"pid":"174be4e08629c3ff6e4d985cee6befde5abcd2e3","tid":1681181,"uid":130565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"屋企隔離😂。聽日試下"},{"pid":"8924d41415ea3d2f6ee1ad71c55ec59fe2c3f038","tid":1681181,"uid":85799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777adbd0cc812eb22be628a7a6b8bb4416436cec","tid":1681181,"uid":73541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"支持，佢地豬軟骨最出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239d530b9c1d71a0a6cd17afc5b76d047ba7fad5","tid":1681181,"uid":188907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco